  "text": "The electrostatic calculations together with the dipole moments and related analysis were performed by using the GRASP software [CITATION_1] running on Silicon Graphics Workstations. The potential maps were calculated with a simplified Poisson-Boltzmann solver [CITATION_2] on the basis of an AMBER-derived parameter file.",
